7-1:  English to metric unit conversion
Preliminary Specification
7/29/2014 LBC

7-1 is a program to convert English to metric units.  When the program is run
it will prompt the user for the English unit of measure and value.  It outputs
the resultant metric equivalent.

The following conversions are valid:
English			Metric
yard			meter
gallon			liter
pound			kilogram

Example:

./7.1
(1) Yards to Meters
(2) Gallons to Liters
(3) Pounds to Kilograms
Select an English to metric conversion: 1
Enter the number of yards:  1
1 yard is 0.9144 meters
